{"tid":921074,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"而家仲有冇人會叫天水圍做悲情城市？","createTime":"2018-11-29T09:45:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T11:19:12.000Z","uid":224175,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a03d4e5eda73e92a518c472e47badc5c922c6ed6","tid":921074,"uid":224175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:45:54.000Z","msg":"今日同同事討論住屋問題，我話天水圍係個幾好既上車地方。點知同事話天水圍係悲情城市喎 。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當刻我都唔知俾咩反應佢好。"},{"pid":"566975ba54906d9c126439cb43052c4d9e9e6597","tid":921074,"uid":191650,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:46:38.000Z","msg":"你同學瞓醒未"},{"pid":"66d391aaed7319d3cdbe41b6c6b739be08e74cc9","tid":921074,"uid":30251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:46:55.000Z","msg":"天水圍唔係大陸個邊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7227b6c4823c0fb0ec321f38ffcadd19e600c6b4","tid":921074,"uid":22566,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:48:59.000Z","msg":"依家嘅香港仲有邊到唔悲情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8daea2ddd19b1be773635de9c1b4047e5ff8c7","tid":921074,"uid":191650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"566975ba54906d9c126439cb43052c4d9e9e6597","tid":921074,"uid":191650,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:46:38.000Z","msg":"你同學瞓醒未"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:50:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">事</span>"},{"pid":"65e26945f7746a6f7d33fae7bbf119c277c68dd8","tid":921074,"uid":38216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:50:42.000Z","msg":"今時今日，係俾果啲連天水圍都上唔到車嘅人叫，叫那悲情城市者，自也悲情<br />\n<br />\n其實當年係因為成日有人跳樓，又有套戲講到住天水圍的人好慘情，所以先叫佢做悲情城市<br />\n<br />\n但講跳樓個案，呢幾年喺新聞上見到嘅都係觀塘同東涌，天水圍靜咗好耐了"},{"pid":"a22606f79db01474826a2c386f495a910158e07c","tid":921074,"uid":1139,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:5